## Cost factors for tiling and masonry

Price depends on area size, tile quality, surface preparation, and whether old tiles need removal. Bathroom jobs often cost more due to waterproofing requirements. Get a clear estimate after the mason inspects the site — avoid paying large advances without a written or WhatsApp-confirmed scope.

